                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-32-off137 t17890422-32-cd138"></join>, two ounces of burnt silver, value 10 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890422-32-victim307" type="victimName">
                     John 
